"{\"uid\": \"scmp.com-lifestyle-food-drink-article-3246889-paris-michelin-star-restaurant-inspired-disneys-ratatouille-tour-dargent-reborn-time-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Tour d'Argent already boasts a 320,000-bottle wine cellar, a world-famous duck recipe and a storied 441-year history.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the legendary restaurant in Paris is about to serve up itsplat de r\\u00e9sistance: a front-row view of two of the biggest events of 2024 - the renaissance of Notre Dame Cathedral and the 2024 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999974060643, \"rank\": 2.5939378693115864e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A city landmark unto itself - and an inspiration for the restaurant in the movieRatatouille- the Tour d'Argent reopened in August 2023 after its own renovation, which preserved revered traditions while adapting to the 21st century.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very reassuring for many customers to see that such establishments are still present in our history, and in French gastronomic history,\\\" says owner and chief executive Andre Terrail.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8712267845020618, \"rank\": 0.14511373064566055, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}]}"